# Private instance overlay — registers extra self-hosted model endpoints + extends
# the LiteLLM fallback chain WITHOUT touching public defaults. Instance-specific,
# never published. The committed values.private.example.yaml shows the mechanism;
# the real file (and any private model spec) stays out of git.
values.private.yaml
values.*.private.yaml
stackit/private-instance-models.md

# agent worktrees
.claude/
